Package: xaringanstat
Type: Package
Title:  Templates for xaringan-presentations based on the corporate design of the canton Zurich.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Lo Russo", email = "thomas.lorusso@statistik.ji.zh.ch",role = c("aut", "cre"),
		   person("Andrea", "Schnell", email = "andrea.schnell@statistik.ji.zh.ch",role = c("aut"))
Description: The package contains templates for xaringan-presentations conforming to the cantonal CD-guidelines. Xaringan is an R package which allows to generate slideshows powered by remark.js. 
			After installing the package the templates are available in  the R Studio menu (File -> New File -> R Markdown -> From Template -> Ninja Presentation).
Depends: xaringan
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true